title: Exercise Files for Getting to Know ArcGIS for Desktop (2013)
description:
[Sorry, third attempt on TPB, hopefully this time will work]

Note: THIS IS NOT THE TEXTBOOK (I don't have time to scan that shit). These are the exercise files that accompany "Getting to Know ArcGIS for Desktop" by Michael Law and Amy Collins, ESRI Press (3rd ed., 2013), for use with ArcGIS 10.1 and beyond.

It's essential to have the exercise files, yet used books often don't come with them-- I learned that the hard way.

-ComradeBishop
